| Feature         | PostgreSQL                             | MySQL                                          |
| --------------- | -------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| Type            | Object-relational                      | Relational                                     |
| Best for        | Complex queries, large data, analytics | Web apps, read-heavy apps                      |
| JSON support    | Excellent                              | Good but less advanced                         |
| Performance     | Great for complex operations           | Great for simple/fast queries                  |
| ACID compliance | Always strict                          | Depends on storage engine (InnoDB recommended) |
